    <item>
      <title>勒庞表示法院解除禁令后她将竞选总统</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/world/europe/marine-le-pen-verdict-election-ban-appeal.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上诉法院确认了马琳·勒庞的贪污罪定罪，但缩短了对她当选公职资格的禁令。这意味着这位法国极右翼领导人可以在 2027 年竞选总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/world/europe/marine-le-pen-verdict-election-ban-appeal.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 19:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
